extends layout

block pageTitle
  title About Hedge Wears — Timeless African Elegance

block metaDesc
  meta(name='description' content='Hedge Wears is a modern African fashion house built on simplicity, cultural depth, and timeless designs. Classic pieces rooted in heritage, crafted for the world.')

block content

  //- ─── HERO ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  section.about-hero.hero--image.section(style='background-image: url("https://hedgewears.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/ctaimage.webp")')
    .hero-overlay
    .container
      .about-hero-inner
        span.section-eyebrow Our story
        h1.about-hero-title About Hedge Wears
        p.about-hero-sub A classic African fashion house built on simplicity, cultural depth, and designs that carry aura. Timeless. Intentional. Boundless.

  //- ─── MISSION ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  section.mission.section.section--dark
    .container
      .mission-inner
        .mission-statement
          span.section-eyebrow Our mission
          blockquote.mission-quote
            | &ldquo;To create classic, high-quality clothing rooted in African identity and craftsmanship &mdash; elevating African fashion on the global stage.&rdquo;
        .mission-body
          p Hedge Wears was born from a desire to break free from fleeting fashion trends. To build pieces that carry cultural weight, that last across seasons, and that speak before you do.
          p The name &ldquo;Hedge&rdquo; is deliberate. It represents ambition &mdash; always reaching further. Resilience &mdash; built to withstand, not bend. The pursuit of greatness &mdash; unapologetically forward.
          p We design for Africans and the African diaspora. For creatives and professionals. For those who understand that what you wear is a declaration of who you are. Every collection is a statement of pride, crafted with intention and premium materials that honour the continent&rsquo;s richest traditions.

  //- ─── VALUES (C.R.E.S.T.) ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
  section.values.section
    .container
      .section-header
        span.section-eyebrow What we stand for
        h2.section-title The C.R.E.S.T. Framework
        p.section-subtitle Five values woven into every piece we create.

      .values-grid.values-grid--5
        .value-card
          .value-icon-wrap
            span.value-letter C
          h3.value-title Classic
          p.value-desc Timeless elegance that withstands any trend cycle. We design for the decade, not the season. Every silhouette is structured to endure.

        .value-card
          .value-icon-wrap
            span.value-letter R
          h3.value-title Rooted
          p.value-desc Authentically connected to African heritage. From Kente-accented seams to Mudcloth-inspired prints, our craft draws from the continent&rsquo;s richest traditions.

        .value-card
          .value-icon-wrap
            span.value-letter E
          h3.value-title Empowering
          p.value-desc Clothing that builds confidence, cultural pride, and identity. When you wear Hedge, you carry a legacy &mdash; that is by design, not by accident.

        .value-card
          .value-icon-wrap
            span.value-letter S
          h3.value-title Stylish
          p.value-desc Modern designs with cultural depth and global relevance. Expressive, deliberate, and fashion-forward &mdash; without chasing what is trending today.

        .value-card
          .value-icon-wrap
            span.value-letter T
          h3.value-title Timeless
          p.value-desc Built to endure &mdash; physically, emotionally, aesthetically. Hedge Wears pieces are investments. They age well because they were made well.

  //- ─── ABOUT US LONG-FORM ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  section.about-longform.section.section--muted
    .container
      .about-longform-inner
        .about-longform-header
          span.section-eyebrow Who we are
          h2.section-title Timeless Style. Rooted Identity. Bold Ambition.
        .about-longform-body
          p Hedge Wears is a modern African fashion house redefining identity, excellence, and timeless style. Founded to move beyond fast-fashion noise, we build collections that last &mdash; physically, culturally, and emotionally.
          p Each piece reflects Africa&rsquo;s diverse heritage, crafted with intentional detail and premium materials. Organic cotton, handwoven Kente and Akwete accents, premium linen blends, and brushed gold finishes. Whether a structured linen shirt or a layered gold accessory set, every item tells a story of pride, power, and ambition.
          p Through HedgeCoin &mdash; our loyalty rewards system &mdash; we ensure that loyalty is recognised and rewarded. Every purchase builds value that comes back to you. The more you shop, the more you save.
          p.about-longform-closing Hedge Wears does not follow fashion. Hedge Wears leads it &mdash; boldly, proudly, and timelessly.

  //- ─── HEDGECOIN CALLOUT ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  section.about-hgc.section
    .container
      .about-hgc-inner
        .about-hgc-content
          span.section-eyebrow HedgeCoin Rewards
          h2.section-title Every purchase earns HGC
          p.about-hgc-desc HedgeCoin (HGC) is our loyalty currency &mdash; not a cryptocurrency, a reward for returning customers. Every completed order earns HGC automatically. Redeem it against your next order. Your balance never expires while your account is active.
          a.btn.btn-primary(href=webShopUrl target='_blank' rel='noopener') Start Earning HGC

        .about-hgc-pills
          .hgc-pill
            img.hgc-icon-inline(src='/img/hgc-icon.svg' alt='HGC')
            span Earns on every order
          .hgc-pill
            img.hgc-icon-inline(src='/img/hgc-icon.svg' alt='HGC')
            span Balance never expires
          .hgc-pill
            img.hgc-icon-inline(src='/img/hgc-icon.svg' alt='HGC')
            span Redeems as instant discount
          .hgc-pill
            img.hgc-icon-inline(src='/img/hgc-icon.svg' alt='HGC')
            span Compounds with every shop

  //- ─── JOIN CTA ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  section.cta-banner.section
    .container
      .cta-banner-inner
        h2.cta-banner-title We don&rsquo;t follow trends. We Hedge legacies.
        p.cta-banner-subtitle Discover fashion that carries your heritage forward.
        .cta-banner-actions
          a.btn.btn-white.btn-lg(href=webShopUrl target='_blank' rel='noopener') Shop the Collection
          a.btn.btn-outline-white.btn-lg(href='/contact') Get in Touch
